parameters.description:
Page number of result records.   _default(1); offset=(size*(page-1));_

```javascript
let
    offset = 0
  , page = req.page
;
if (page <= 0)
    page = 1;
if (page > 1)
    offset = ((page-1)*size);
// . . .
```

Limit of result page records count.   _default(16); limit=(size<=0?-1:size+1);_

```javascript
const
    default = 16
  , maximum = 32
;
let limit = req.size;
if (limit <= 0)
    limit = default;
if (maximum < limit)
    limit = maximum;
// . . .
```

